snippet.title: Alt-Frequencies - Live Teaser
snippet.description:
ALT-FREQUENCIES - MAY 2019 (iOS, Android, PC)

➡️ Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1035050/AltFrequencies/

A time loop, a conspiracy and the biggest vote in history. Alt-Frequencies is an audio mystery game where you use the airwaves to open the world’s eyes to the truth.

Record, rewind time and broadcast snippets of radio shows to expose radio hosts, conspiracy theorists, politicians, underground activists - and a dog.

📻 http://altfrequencies.com 📻

Stay tuned.

**********

"Alt-Frequencies" (http://altfrequencies.com) by Accidental Queens (http://www.accidentalqueens.com) & ARTE France (http://www.arte.tv)

Published by Plug in Digital (http://www.plug-in-digital.com/)

Video by Matthieu Corno & Ulysse Tassin (http://www.ulyssetassin.com/)
Sound design by Christopher Knight (http://christopherknight.audio/)
